{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'All clear over here!', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'The CPF casing is open! Come take a look!', 4: '3'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Sophia', 3: 'Status... green. This CPF is in remarkably good condition.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Sophia', 3: 'It should reactivate in no time.', 4: '1'}
{2: "You're good at this, Sophia.", 3: '14'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Sophia', 3: 'The CPF we have in Asslam breaks a lot...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Sophia', 3: "...At least since Chief Andre's been gone.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Sophia', 3: 'No matter. With the help of Babylonia, Asslam has received enough parts now.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Sophia', 3: 'No need to worry.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Oh my—! Get over here, guys!', 4: '3'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Kamui, yooo, get a load of this!', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Ohmygod ohmygod ohmygod! Is this the—', 4: '3'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "—The Mogpal Combat Bible! The limited edition director's cut, too!", 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "Ooh! And there's a... Knight Weapon Complex BRM-16 model gun! And metal!!", 4: '3'}
{2: 'Put the toy gun down, Kamui...', 3: '30'}
{2: 'Fox in a henhouse, indeed...', 3: '31'}
{1: '1', 3: "Guess it's better to let these two enjoy their new toys."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Commandant, over here.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 3: "The tip of Lucia's blade points at a dead body spread-eagle on the ground, already stiff."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Probably dead for a while. Must have starved to death.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'This must be the "King". How did he end up like this?', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "I heard that humans could develop hallucinations when extremely hungry. They could see things that don't exist.", 4: '3'}
{2: '...trapped in his own kingdom.', 3: '45'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "...I'll contact Babylonia and tell them that it's all clear here.", 4: '2'}
